Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:09.70,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要踏出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.80,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}世界就会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.24,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}想象外的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.50,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}也能现于眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.77,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只需相信便好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:25.55,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}铁杵尚能磨成针
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.77,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}你我一定也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:30.76,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要我们在一起
